# 🎧 NeuroAmp DSP

> Professional DSP + Spatial Audio Engine for Android

---

## 🚀 Features
- 🎚 Parametric Equalizer (multi-band)
- 🔊 FIR Convolution Engine
- 🌌 Spatial Audio + Head Tracking
- 🧠 Adaptive AI Sound Tuning
- 🚗 Car Audio Optimization (India-focused)

---

## 📱 Supported Platforms
- Android phones
- Android head units
- Android TV (experimental)

---

## 🧠 Architecture

Flutter UI → Kotlin Bridge → C++ DSP Engine → Oboe Audio

